Package org.lanter.lan4gate.Messages.Notification

Interface INotification

All Known Implementing Classes:
Notification
public interface INotification
This interface provide access for notification events from terminal. You can use this interface in two cases: 1. Get only notification code and display your own message considering additional info 2. Get message text and display directly.
